            "block": "paragraph",
            "content": [
                "This block provides a CSS class that implements the ",
                {
                    "block": "strong",
                    "content": "clearfix"
                },
                " layout hack, also known as the ",
                {
                    "href": "http://www.456bereastreet.com/archive/200603/new_clearing_method_needed_for_ie7/",
                    "block": "link",
                    "content": "Easy Clearing Method"
                },
                ". The hack allows you to clear wrapping for elements with the CSS ",
                {
                    "block": "inline-code",
                    "content": "float"
                },
                " property, without making any changes to the document's original HTML structure."
            ]
        },
        {
            "block": "paragraph",
            "content": [
                "This block can be used as a container for elements with the ",
                {
                    "block": "inline-code",
                    "content": "float"
                },
                " property, or mixed with such a container."
            ]
        },
        {
            "block": "paragraph",
            "content": "Example when used as a container:"
        },
        {
            "block": "html",
            "content": "<!-- bem-example: tmp/data/bem-core-4.2.1/touch-phone.examples/clearfix/NurIrTuYiSPj742DQi8qLSWIZ20 -->"
        },
        {
            "block": "paragraph",
            "content": "Mixed with a container block:"
